{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CLPytQCZ2ELYtVVqDb61Bg","type":"tool_result","content":"170-\n171----\n172-\n173:### Decision 3: Agent Abstraction — Ralph Becomes One Implementation\n174-\n175-**Problem:** 28 files reference Ralph directly. State files are written by bash, read by TypeScript. No versioned contract. If Ralph is replaced, 28 files break.\n176-\n177:**Decision:** Create an `AgentDriver` interface. Ralph becomes one implementation. Future drivers (direct Claude API, other LLM CLIs) can be added.\n178-\n179-```typescript\n180:// src/lib/agents/types.ts\n181:interface AgentDriver {\n182-  readonly name: string;\n183-  spawn(opts: SpawnOpts): AgentProcess;\n184-  parseOutput(line: string): AgentEvent | null;\n--\n205-\n206-**File structure:**\n207-```\n208:src/lib/agents/\n209:├── types.ts          # AgentDriver, AgentProcess, AgentEvent interfaces\n210:├── ralph.ts          # RalphDriver implements AgentDriver (wraps ralph.sh)\n211-├── stream-parser.ts  # Moved from src/lib/ — parses Claude stream-json\n212-└── __tests__/\n213-```\n214-\n215-**What changes:**\n216:- `run.ts` imports `AgentDriver` instead of directly spawning ralph\n217-- `run-helpers.ts` merges into `ralph.ts` (ralph-specific parsing)\n218-- `ralph-prompt.ts` moves into `ralph.ts`\n219-- State files (`.story_retries`, `.flagged_stories`) are managed by TypeScript, not bash\n--\n241-│   ├── nodejs.ts\n242-│   ├── python.ts\n243-│   └── rust.ts\n244:├── agents/           # Decision 3 — agent drivers\n245-│   ├── index.ts\n246-│   ├── types.ts\n247-│   ├── ralph.ts\n--\n575-│   └── ...\n576-├── lib/                # Shared utilities (domain subdirectories)\n577-│   ├── stacks/         # Stack provider pattern (Decision 2)\n578:│   ├── agents/         # Agent driver pattern (Decision 3)\n579-│   ├── coverage/       # Coverage detection, execution, parsing\n580-│   ├── docker/         # Docker compose, health, cleanup\n581-│   ├── observability/  # OTLP instrumentation, backend queries\n--\n741-- Move business logic from commands to modules\n742-- Add boundary tests\n743-\n744:**Phase 4: Agent Abstraction (Epic 13)**\n745:- Create AgentDriver interface\n746-- Wrap Ralph behind it\n747-- Move ralph-specific parsing into ralph driver\n748-\n--\n771-|-----|----------|\n772-| 5+ state files, no sync | Decision 1 (Unified State) |\n773-| 41 stack conditionals | Decision 2 (Stack Provider) |\n774:| 28 files coupled to Ralph | Decision 3 (Agent Abstraction) |\n775-| lib/ is a flat dumping ground | Decision 4 (lib/ Restructuring) |\n776-| Hardcoded VictoriaMetrics | Decision 5 (Backend Choice) |\n777-| Retro items never actioned | Decision 6 (Retro-to-Sprint Pipeline) |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Jf4NVSZHxoiSr5pCRGQCHS","session_id":"8c35c2f7-0e10-4994-a438-2b5cecce3396","uuid":"43b5201b-e034-4e48-b30a-00ca87c42225","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:28:37.974Z"}
