{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01URpoBxRqF4AaoBNkrPMWY7","type":"tool_result","content":"   104→\n   105→### 12-4-shared-test-utilities-fixtures — code-review (2026-03-24T18:25:00Z)\n   106→\n   107→- MEDIUM (fixed): `createStateMock()` exported phantom functions `readLocalConfig` and `getProjectRoot` that don't exist in codebase. Split into `createStateMock()` and `createSprintStateMock()`.\n   108→- MEDIUM (fixed): Unused `StoryStatus` type import in `state-builders.ts`.\n   109→- MEDIUM (fixed): Inaccurate JSDoc on `createStateMock()` claiming to match two modules while mixing real and nonexistent functions.\n   110→- LOW (unfixed): `selector.test.ts` wraps shared builders in local helpers rather than using `buildSprintState` directly.\n   111→- LOW (unfixed): No `index.ts` barrel file in `src/lib/__tests__/fixtures/` — consumers must know `helpers.ts` re-export convention.\n   112→- Architecture concern: Mock factories cannot be used with `vi.mock()` directly due to Vitest hoisting — pattern's value limited until more test files refactored.\n   113→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8c35c2f7-0e10-4994-a438-2b5cecce3396","uuid":"4de7ce35-8407-43a2-8e11-ad4a6e1f6da6","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:30:05.087Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"\n### 12-4-shared-test-utilities-fixtures — code-review (2026-03-24T18:25:00Z)\n\n- MEDIUM (fixed): `createStateMock()` exported phantom functions `readLocalConfig` and `getProjectRoot` that don't exist in codebase. Split into `createStateMock()` and `createSprintStateMock()`.\n- MEDIUM (fixed): Unused `StoryStatus` type import in `state-builders.ts`.\n- MEDIUM (fixed): Inaccurate JSDoc on `createStateMock()` claiming to match two modules while mixing real and nonexistent functions.\n- LOW (unfixed): `selector.test.ts` wraps shared builders in local helpers rather than using `buildSprintState` directly.\n- LOW (unfixed): No `index.ts` barrel file in `src/lib/__tests__/fixtures/` — consumers must know `helpers.ts` re-export convention.\n- Architecture concern: Mock factories cannot be used with `vi.mock()` directly due to Vitest hoisting — pattern's value limited until more test files refactored.\n","numLines":10,"startLine":104,"totalLines":113}}}
